# Build
/build/
*.o
*.elf

# Vendored stdlib — repopulated by `cyrius deps` from the
# version-pinned snapshot in cyrius.cyml [deps] stdlib. Keeping
# this out of the repo prevents stale stubs from a prior cyrius
# version sitting in tree (matches agnosys/yukti/patra convention).
/lib/

# Rust legacy — `rust-old/` removed in v1.3.2 (port-arc + audit cycle
# complete; ADR-001 + benchmarks-rust-v-cyrius.md + git history of the
# v0.x→v1.0.0 commits carry the historical record). Build-artifact
# patterns kept here as safety in case anyone restores the dir from
# an older commit for benchmark re-runs.
rust-old/

